<s> Doc_816141_0_11_Chemical-induced immune Doc_816141_27_43_Disease. </s>
<s> A patient with Doc_816141_60_73_Disease developed Coombs-positive Doc_816141_100_116_Disease while receiving Doc_816141_133_144_Chemical therapy. </s>
<s> An anti-Doc_816141_162_173_Chemical IgG antibody was detected in the patient's serum and in the eluates from her erythrocytes. </s>
