<s> Skin tests and in vitro lymphocyte stimulation revealed that the patient was sensitized to Doc_816141_500_511_Chemical and also to Doc_816141_524_534_Chemical. </s>
<s> Careful investigation of drug-induced Doc_816141_574_591_Disease reveals the complexity of the immune mechanisms involved. </s>
